data.description: This mid-century modern gem is perched at the end of a tree lined street located in the charming Miraleste section of Rancho Palos Verdes. Perfectly suited for entertaining, the property consists of a sprawling 3 bedroom 3.25 bathroom single level resort style layout. Upon entry there is gorgeous terrazzo floor that leads to the kitchen. The kitchen consists of beautiful custom cabinets, updated hardwood floor, granite counter tops and stainless-steel appliances. The formal dining room branches off the kitchen that features amazing nighttime views of the city lights.   Adjacent to dining room you will find the family room which has a brick fireplace with a large sliding door that offers direct access to back yard and pool area along with a custom wet bar. There are two large bedrooms as you continue down the hallway that include spacious closets with a full Jack and Jill bathroom. You will then arrive at the master bathroom which includes beautiful white tiled floors with a large Terrazzo tub and shower with a window that peers into a private courtyard. The oversized master bedroom includes one large walk-in closet and another mirrored closet directly across the room. The wide-open backyard is covered with pavers surrounding a beautiful swimming pool. There is gorgeous landscaping all around that offers a very private and quiet environment for relaxing. Along the side of the home there are a variety of fruit trees and area for gardening. This location offers great views, great weather, and access to the award-winning Palos Verdes school district.
